caption: A small metal cube rests on a polished wooden floor, its sleek surface reflecting the warm tones of the wood. Suddenly, it begins to glide smoothly across the floor. The subtle sound of metal against wood accompanies its journey, creating a rhythmic pattern as it continues its path across the room.
